0.014: Add response plurk function.
0.015: Reformated source code and remove unused responseform tag. 
0.016: Code optimization, fix plurk without responsed always display as unread bug. Known issue: if click on slidesbar icon twice too quick, refresh will hang.
0.017: Fix a bug causing continuous reload when refresh new plurk since 016.
0.018: Sending plurk function.

-Known issue-
* Sometimes open response will failed occasionally.
* Continuous multiple plurks from the same person will show only one, due to bug of plurk API.
* Set read status to plurk with response malfunction due to bug of plurk API.